{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_12_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 2話 こころは見てないですよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――合同撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― On the day of the joint shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "お、来ましたね、{user}さん。こころと\n愛ちゃんの撮影が待ち切れなかったんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you’re here‚ {user}. You couldn't wait\nfor the shoot with Kokoro and Ai-chan‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9666667383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "待ち切れないのはこころの方だろう？\n撮影までまだ時間があるのに随分早く来たじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't you the one who couldn't wait‚ Kokoro?\nYou’re here quite early‚ even though there's time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6333334049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "というか雨の予報で、屋内での撮影になっただろう\nどうして外に……まさか俺を迎えに来てくれたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ the shoot moved indoors due to the rain forecast.\nWhy are you outside… Did you come to meet me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6007596255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.0666667383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "その通りです。{user}さんがスタジオで\nこころを見つけられなかったら大変ですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. It would be a disaster if you\ncouldn't find Kokoro in the studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.6000000716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが寂しくて泣いちゃうかも\nそう考えたら可哀想に思えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might even cry from loneliness.\nThinking about that made me feel pity for you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺は子供じゃないんだぞ……\nまぁ、ありがとう、待たせて悪かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not a child‚ you know…\nAnyway‚ thanks. Sorry for making you wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9641470463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.5000000716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "感謝して下さいよ～？\nそれじゃお礼にオフショを撮って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should be grateful‚ okay~?\nThen‚ take some off-shots of me as a reward!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "オフショ……って、もしかしなくても\n最初からそれが目的で待っていたな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Off-shots… Wait‚ I bet that was\nyour goal for waiting here all along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.0666667383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、せっかくの撮影なんですから\nSNSに載せる用の写真もほしいじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ since it's a shoot anyway‚\nI need photos to post on social media too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.9000000716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "それに外での撮影の方がこの衣装は合うと思うんです\nいや、むしろ外で撮るべきです！　もったいないです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I think this outfit suits outdoor shoots better.\nNo‚ we HAVE to take photos outside! It’s a waste!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "不思議なことにこーんなに可愛い素敵な傘を！\n親切な誰かさんがプレゼントしてくれたんですし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially since I have this incredibly cute umbrella!\nSomeone very kind gave it to me as a gift!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7666667383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ということで、ほらほら早く撮って下さいよ～\n可愛いこころをまだ待たせる気ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ come on‚ hurry up and take the photos~\nAre you going to keep a cute girl like me waiting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6333334049,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10876.666666700004,
          "startTime": 95.5100000716
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.9058133625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。撮影まで時間があるし、少しなら……\nじゃあ早速一枚……よし、これでいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine. We have time before the shoot‚ so just a few…\nLet's start with one… Alright‚ is this good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9058133625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.0666667383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "お～、モデルがいいのもありますが、意外とやりおーる\nでは次はもっとアイドルスマイル全開で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~ The model is great‚ but you're surprisingly good at this.\nNow‚ the next one with full-on idol smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2666667383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、今のいい感じですね！\nこの調子であと百枚は撮りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm-hmm‚ that last one felt really good!\nAt this rate‚ let's take a hundred more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺のスマホの写真フォルダを\nこころで一杯にする気か。程よく切り上げるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you trying to fill up my\nphone's photo folder with you? Let's wrap this up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.2333308618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　つれないですね～\nむしろ、スマホの容量一杯まで撮りましょうよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh—? You're so cold~\nLet's keep going until your phone storage is full~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9999975284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.0999975284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "よーやくノッてきたところなんですから\nほらほら、こういうポーズも幻想的で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m finally getting into the groove now.\nCome on‚ look‚ even this pose is fantastic…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0999975284,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11866.66920990001,
          "startTime": 141.9666667383
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……いえ、やっぱりもうスタジオに行きましょう\n{user}さん、荷物持ったままですしね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… wait‚ actually‚ let's head to the studio now.\nYou’re carrying all those bags‚ after all‚ {user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5999975284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2666621606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こころ？　急にどうしたんだ……？　あっちに何か……\nあれ？　あそこにいる子達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro? What's wrong all of a sudden…? Is something there?\nOh? Those girls over there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5979761072,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4402.021421200005,
          "startTime": 151.9999975284
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.7499975284
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.7499975284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ、こころ。さっき外で、こころと\n同じ学校の制服を着た子達を見かけたんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ Kokoro. Outside‚ I saw some girls\nwearing the same school uniform as you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0333308618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.5999975284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　そんな人いました？\nこころは見てないですよ、気のせいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh—? Were there people like that?\nKokoro didn't see them. You're just imagining it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3666641951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.2666641951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あの子達はこころのことを見ていたと思うが……\nやっぱり学校で何かあったんじゃないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think those girls were looking at you‚ though…\nDid something really happen at school after all…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.0999975284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.0333288272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "だから知らないですって～！\nそれより、もうすぐ愛ちゃんとの撮影ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said I don't know anything about it~!\nMore importantly‚ the shoot with Ai-chan is starting soon!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.5333288272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.7333288272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "いーっぱい気合い入れて頑張っちゃいますから！\nでも……その愛ちゃんがどこにもいないんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going to give it my all!\nBut… Ai-chan is nowhere to be found.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.9999954939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ……そのことなんだが、さっき愛の現場から\n連絡があってな。愛の収録がかなり押しているらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… about that‚ I just got a call\nfrom Ai's team. Her recording is running very late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.2666621606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.9333288272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、じゃあ今日の撮影は……？\nもうすぐ撮影の時間になっちゃうのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Then today's shoot is…?\nIt's almost time for us to start…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.3666621606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.6666621606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "この後、スタッフさん達に掛け合ってみるが\n愛だけ別日の撮影になる可能性もあり得るな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll talk to the staff later‚ but\nthere's a chance Ai might have to film on another day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.8658117692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.5666621606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……せっかくkanaさんにお願いして……\nいいトリートメントまで用意してセットしたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way… I even asked kana-san for a favor…\nand prepared a special hair treatment for this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.5666621606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "こんなことになってしまってすまない\nあんなに楽しみにしてくれていたのにな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry it turned out like this.\nYou were looking forward to it so much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.3999954939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 222.3666621606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
