      "text": "どうして{user}さんが謝るんですか\n仕方のないことじゃないですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you apologizing‚ {user}?\nIt couldn't be helped…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.4333288272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 228.1999954939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってお互いに忙しいのは分かってましたし\nこういうアクシデントが起きることもありますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew we'd both be busy after becoming BIG4.\nThese kinds of accidents happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.3333288272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 235.5999954939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です、こころ一人でもBIG4のリズノワだって\n他のアイドル達にしっかり分からせてやりますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine. Even alone‚ I'll show the other idols\nthat I am the LizNoir of the BIG4!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.1333288272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.1333288272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "それにまだ……可能性はありますもんね\n愛ちゃんのこと……ギリギリまで待ちますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ there's still… a chance.\nAi-chan… I'll wait for her until the very end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.5666621606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（気丈に振る舞ってくれてはいるが）\n（明らかにこころの元気がなくなってしまった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's acting tough‚ but）\n（Kokoro has clearly lost her energy…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.5333288272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 257.8333267927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "こころ……愛のリスケが確定したよ\n愛の撮影は、後日行う流れになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro… Ai's rescheduling is confirmed.\nWe've decided to film Ai's part on another day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.2333288272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
