      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 281.2333410342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（BIG4になったことで周りからも一線引かれているし）\n（なんとかサポート出来ればいいんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And people are keeping their distance since she became BIG4.）\n（I wish I could support her somehow…）",
