      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_02-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "まだ……私の順番まで時間ありましたよね\n少しだけ頭冷やしてきますから……すぐ戻ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still have time… before my turn‚ right?\nI'll go clear my head for a bit… I'll be back soon.",
        "id": ""
